is very strong. With the help of Flipkart, we, working here in Surat, are selling all over the country!<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"6fef375\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6d1aec1\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7d2044a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3>Building a community while growing a business<\\/h3><p>In the beginning, I was alone, and ran my small business single-handedly. Then, as I expanded the business, I hired more people. Today, I have a lot of employees with me. However, my employees are not just employees to me but like my real family, and we enjoy a bond of togetherness.<\\/p><p>My entire family is very proud of my achievements. When other people\\u2019s children were going to college, I had already set up my entire business! With the help of Flipkart, I intend to take my business to the next level. I feel very confident today, and my message to other sellers is to partner with Flipkart and take your business and life forward!<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"3944638\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"17993ca\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4cd50ae\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text\":\"Divider\",\"gap\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":11,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"divider\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c8549d2\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a3b69ee\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d14d556\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><em>To read more stories of #SellfMade Flipkart sellers like Mohit Vaghela, click\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/stories.flipkart.com\\/sellers\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">here<\\/a>.<\\/em><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
