 We cater to every category within the beauty and grooming segment: we have fragrance, personal care, skin care, make-up, and also men\\u2019s grooming.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1bcdc07\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"643fa29\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c8b4dba\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3>Moment of truth: Going from employee to entrepreneur<\\/h3><p>After finishing my college, I worked for two years in a hair care company. After that, I joined a make-up company for 3 months. However, in the span of those 3 months, I took that brand from \\u200b\\u200b\\u20b94 lakh to \\u20b940 lakh. That\\u2019s when I decided that if I can do this for another brand, why don\\u2019t I do this for my own company? Then I met my current business partner, Tarun. And we got together to create our own business strategy.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4764275\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4a65578\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0753cbf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3>An ace online seller on Flipkart<\\/h3><p>Flipkart is one of the best platforms out there. And the registration process was surprisingly so smooth. Flipkart\\u2019s seller support and our account managers provided us with a lot of help. From how to upload images, which images to upload, and what keywords to use to make our listings rise \\u2013 I learned a lot from them. They also gave us insights on how to best optimize Flipkart ads, among other things. All of this really helped us grow.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9ac906c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"46e477b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ea4d733\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3>Heading towards an impact-led future<\\/h3><p>When we started, we started with two people. And now in two years we are a team of 40 people. Flipkart is one of the best platforms out there where you can grow \\u2013 you can create a name for yourself. Today, through Flipkart, I am getting a chance to share my story with millions of people. I hope my story inspires many others.<\\/p><p>To read more success stories in India, click\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/stories.flipkart.com\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">here<\\/a>.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
